data.description: *OFFER ACCEPTED* Situated on a spacious half-acre lot, this 3-bedroom home provides ample space for outdoor activities and plenty of room to roam. Inside, you'll find laminate wood floors that not only add a touch of elegance but also make cleaning a breeze. This low-maintenance flooring is perfect for those with busy lifestyles or anyone looking for a stylish and durable option. The open-island kitchen is perfect for those who love to cook and entertain at the same time. It offers plenty of counter space, storage, and modern appliances, allowing you to unleash your culinary creativity. And if location is everything, this property is situated just 5 miles from downtown Burleson and only 20 miles from downtown Fort Worth. You'll have easy access to all the amenities and attractions the city has to offer while still enjoying the tranquility of living outside city limits. Whether it's shopping, dining, or cultural experiences, everything is within reach.
